    <div class="guarantee">
        <div class="guarantee__container container">
            <img src="assets/img/guarentee.png" alt="100% Satisfaction Guarentee" class="slide-in">
            <h3>We guarantee that once we get to them, those pesky mosquitoes will be gone. And if they come back, so will we. It's our promise.</h3>
            <p>We’re committed to keeping your home and business mosquito free!. We’ll do whatever it takes to keep them out.</p>
